{"tid":401832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【民主牆風波】湯家驊斥不應姑息港獨言論：慈母多敗兒","createTime":"2017-09-16T02:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T07:25:03.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0a53725e1a01129c8e2a4e15e1a21f12903b164","tid":401832,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170916/large/1505529349_005e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170916%2Flarge%2F1505529349_005e.png&h=b77964b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日多間大專院校出現支持港獨的宣傳品，身兼行政會議成員的民主思路召集人湯家驊表明，言論既有自由亦有責任，港人絕不應該姑息港獨言論，否則只會是「慈母多敗兒」。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊今早在商台節目中重申言論自由是有權有責，2003年社會反對《基本法》廿三條立法，因當時並無人站出來挑戰中央在香港行使主權的地位，但如今形勢有變。他建議政府應修改《刑事罪行》第9和第10條，指當有人展示涉及暴力或犯法的標語，即應當作觸犯刑事法例處理，並建議授權持有業權的場地持份者可以拆除別人在該處展示的港獨宣傳品。"},{"pid":"3e5668051740546ea227acbeb6d13d336280dd7c","tid":401832,"uid":17697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"又係呢條奶共驊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a62d1316cd08b6254d559bc2406c01e9a3ef331","tid":401832,"uid":20170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淚</span></span>"},{"pid":"bfb5868883154ccaa228ab61401719be11522312","tid":401832,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"衰"},{"pid":"306d8834a2d7e6d63a67c6445d5659855593ccc0","tid":401832,"uid":5945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淚</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">灑</span></span>"},{"pid":"3a355df271aebceb940c6034a6d798fae9317d58","tid":401832,"uid":6